# Custom Docker images

Homelab custom images are **not** built from this repo. Each image has its own GitHub repository and `Build Image` workflow; CI publishes to GHCR.

| Image | Source repo | GHCR |
|-------|-------------|------|
| hermes-homelab | [nerddotdad/hermes-homelab](https://github.com/nerddotdad/hermes-homelab) | `ghcr.io/nerddotdad/hermes-homelab` |
| homelab-alert-bridge | [nerddotdad/homelab-alert-bridge](https://github.com/nerddotdad/homelab-alert-bridge) | `ghcr.io/nerddotdad/homelab-alert-bridge` |

## truecharts (this repo)

- Pin `image.repository` + semver `tag` (and digest when Renovate opens PRs) in HelmRelease / Deployment manifests under `clusters/`.
- Do **not** add Docker sources or image build workflows here.

## Image repos

- Edit `Dockerfile`, sources, and `VERSION` in the dedicated repo.
- `.github/workflows/build-image.yml` bumps patch `VERSION` on push (unless you edited `VERSION` in the commit) and pushes to GHCR.
- Manual rebuild: **Actions → Build Image → Run workflow** in the image repo.
